      "message": "I don\u0027t feel too strongly about this; having it as a VA from the paint color would help batching in the GrFillRectOp, but we know that\u0027s not really likely to happen unless they redraw the exact same image. In that case, I wonder if one uniform may offer better performance than expanding it out to a color per vertex that\u0027s only used to draw 2 triangles?",
